PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FFor the latest in our series of
OL,7,Freports about TBI, ITV News' Geraint
OL,8,FVincent reports on why some British
OL,9,Fveterans are turning to America for
OL,10,Fhelp
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Senior News Editor,
OL,13,FPaul Tyson
OL,15,FThe Special Air Service Association
OL,16,Fhas launched a scheme to send special
OL,17,Fforces veterans with blast-induced
OL,18,FTraumatic Brain Injury (TBI) to the
OL,19,FUnited States for diagnosis and
OL,20,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FBlast TBI can be caused by major
OL,7,Fexplosions but also by repeated
OL,8,Fexposure to low-level blast over a
OL,9,Fperiod of time. Symptoms often emerge
OL,10,Fmany years after the exposure that
OL,11,Fcaused them.
OL,13,FThree SAS veterans have confirmed to
OL,14,FITV News that their Regimental
OL,15,FAssociation - an organisation that
OL,16,Facts as a bridge between the Regiment
OL,17,Fand its veteran community - has told
OL,18,Fmembers who may be suffering symptoms
OL,19,Fthat help is available.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FIn keeping with the Special Forces
OL,7,Funit's reputation for secrecy details
OL,8,Fof the scheme are not public however
OL,9,Fthe Regiment is known to work closely
OL,10,Fwith Special Operations Command in
OL,11,FAmerica where Blast TBI has long been
OL,12,Frecognised as a serious problem
OL,13,Faffecting operators and veterans.
OL,15,FIn the US veterans with symptoms can
OL,16,Fundergo advanced MEG brain scans which
OL,17,Fcan detect the microscopic
OL,18,Fneurological damage caused by blast
OL,19,Fexposure that traditional MRI or CT
OL,20,Fscans cannot see.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FThere is no cure for Blast TBI but
OL,7,Fthere are a promising range of
OL,8,Ftreatments in development that use
OL,9,Fneuro-stimulation to help the brain
OL,10,Frepair itself.
OL,12,FIn the UK, veterans rely on the NHS
OL,13,Fwhere few doctors have any knowledge
OL,14,Fof the effects of blast and TBI is
OL,15,Falmost never diagnosed unless there is
OL,16,Fevidence of a "typical" head injury.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FMEG scanners are not approved for
OL,7,Fclinical use and the Government
OL,8,Fbelieves more research is needed
OL,9,Fbefore they recognise the condition.
OL,10,FAs a result British veterans are
OL,11,Froutinely diagnosed with PTSD or other
OL,12,Fpsychiatric conditions, even where
OL,13,Fthey have clear neurological symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FThe SAS Association's move to fund
OL,7,Fdiagnosis and treatment for their
OL,8,Fveterans in America will be seen as a
OL,9,Fclear signal that at least some in the
OL,10,FUK military are not prepared to wait
OL,11,Ffor the NHS to catch up with
OL,12,Fscientific advances in the rest of the
OL,13,Fworld.
OL,15,FMatt Hellyer served for 25 years with
OL,16,Fthe Special Air Service, including
OL,17,Foperational tours of Sierra Leone,
OL,18,FAfghanistan and Iraq. He said that for
OL,19,Fspecial forces soldiers exposure to
OL,20,Fblast is almost routine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FOf his time in Iraq he said: "I
OL,7,Funderwent 400 operations on those
OL,8,Ftours, that's three operations a day.
OL,9,FThat's not including the training that
OL,10,Fwe're doing when we're not on
OL,11,Foperations. That is a six month period
OL,12,Fof condensed breaching, explosions,
OL,13,Floud bangs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,F"The distance between the explosion
OL,7,Fand the assaulting troops is very
OL,8,Fsmall because we are working in small
OL,9,Fteams, we need to get through gaps and
OL,10,Fholes that are created by explosions
OL,11,Fextremely fast. So the distances
OL,12,Fbetween the explosions and the rest of
OL,13,Fthe troops is very small.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,F"The amount of ringing in your ears
OL,7,Fyou get after a day on operations is
OL,8,Fconstant. And we are seeing this now
OL,9,Fthat a lot of our veterans are
OL,10,Fsuffering or have been diagnosed with
OL,11,FPTSD and we question this because some
OL,12,Fof the people that are being
OL,13,Fdiagnosed, and I'm not a medical
OL,14,Fexpert, but I know what PTSD looks
OL,15,Flike. And in some of these cases it is
OL,16,Fnot PTSD that I see in some of my
OL,17,Fcomrades and colleagues."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMr Hellyer welcomed the move to fund
OL,12,Fdiagnosis and treatment in America. He
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Special Air Service
OL,14,FAssociation is a forward-leaning
OL,15,Forganisation, as the unit is. They're
OL,16,Flooking at the evidence and they're
OL,17,Ftrying to understand what the problem
OL,18,Fis. It's not just psychiatric or
OL,19,Fpsychological. There is a physical
OL,20,Finjury."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,F"The US have identified this as being
OL,7,Fa problem within their military and
OL,8,Fthey've put in protocols now for
OL,9,Fexplosions, for demolitions operatives
OL,10,Fand people firing large-calibre
OL,11,Fammunition, such as the .50 calibre,
OL,12,Fand there are restrictions on how many
OL,13,Fexplosions they can face, how many
OL,14,Frounds that they can fire because it
OL,15,Fis damaging people's brains physically.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,F"I know that UK Special Forces, and
OL,7,FI'm not a spokesman for them, but I
OL,8,Fjust know that they are looking at
OL,9,Fthese explosions and they are trying
OL,10,Fto limit the exposure that the troops
OL,11,Fare getting to give duty of care back
OL,12,Finto our servicemen and women."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FMr Hellyer now runs a small charity
OL,7,Fcalled Pilgrim Bandits which aims to
OL,8,Fhelp military and blue-light veterans.
OL,9,FThe charity has funded advanced brain
OL,10,Fscans for ten veterans from various
OL,11,Fregiments. In each case the patient
OL,12,Fhad a prior diagnosis of PTSD and in
OL,13,Feach case the scan showed physical
OL,14,Fdamage to the brain.
OL,16,FHe called for support to expand MEG
OL,17,Fscanning to other veterans with
OL,18,Frelevant symptoms and said he hoped
OL,19,Fthe SAS Association's move would
OL,20,Fpressure the big military charities to
OL,21,Fget involved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FHe said: "There's obviously money
OL,7,Finvolved, you know, the scans do cost
OL,8,Fmoney. It's not a huge amount in the
OL,9,Fgrand scheme of things, but for a
OL,10,Fsmall charity like us, it is a lot of
OL,11,Fmoney. That has a huge impact on us.
OL,12,FAnd we've got other things to do as
OL,13,Fwell.
OL,15,F"With the amount of money that's in
OL,16,Fthe military charitable sector, you
OL,17,Fknow, there's a lot of money in this
OL,18,Fsector. It shouldn't be left down to
OL,19,Fthe small charities."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FCampaigners for Blast TBI to be
OL,7,Frecognised and treated in the UK have
OL,8,Falso praised the SAS Association. Kate
OL,9,FEngland, whose husband James served in
OL,10,Fthe Queen's Dragoon Guards and now has
OL,11,Fneurological damage, said she hoped
OL,12,Fthe move would pressure the government
OL,13,Fand the big military charities to take
OL,14,Faction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FShe said: "This is not rocket science
OL,7,Fto put two and two together here yet
OL,8,Fthe other services still aren't
OL,9,Frecognising this, the MoD still aren't
OL,10,Frecognising this, NHS services still
OL,11,Faren't recognising this, the big
OL,12,Fcharities, the military aren't
OL,13,Frecognising this and they aren't doing
OL,14,Fanything for it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "The health and
OL,8,Fwellbeing of our Armed Forces is
OL,9,Fcritical, and we provide specialist
OL,10,Fmedical treatment for Traumatic Brain
OL,11,FInjuries at the Defence Medical
OL,12,FRehabilitation Centre.
OL,14,F"We are actively working with our
OL,15,Finternational partners on advancing
OL,16,Fthe diagnosis, management and
OL,17,Frehabilitation of patients with Mild
OL,18,FTraumatic Brain Injury, which will
OL,19,Fhelp both military and civilian
OL,20,Fpatients.
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775873035
OL,3,CSAS veterans fly to US for brain
OL,4,Cinjury treatment unavailable in the UK
OL,6,F"This includes investing #3.65m in the
OL,7,Fworld's first mobile quantum-enabled
OL,8,Fmagnetoencephalography (MEG) brain
OL,9,Fscanner, built in the UK and able to
OL,10,Ftell us what happens in the minutes
OL,11,Fand hours after blast exposure.
OL,13,F"Later this year, we will publish the
OL,14,Ffirst Acquired Brain Injury Action
OL,15,FPlan to set out the action needed to
OL,16,Fhelp improve the lives of people who
OL,17,Fhave experienced an acquired brain
OL,18,Finjury."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
